document_data.mainbody: '''Morningstar Haven''' was a temple dedicated to [[Lathander]] located in the city of [[Westgate]] in [[1367 DR]].
document_data.Location: The temple was located on [[Westgate Market Street]] in the northwest section of the city next to the [[House of Ilmater]].
